===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|cole}}, from {{inh|en|ang|col}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*kulą}} (compare {{cog|fy|koal}}, {{cog|nl|kool}}, {{cog|de|Kohle}}, {{cog|da|kul}}), from {{der|en|ine-pro|*gʷol-}} (compare {{cog|sga|gúal||coal}}, {{cog|txb|śoliye||hearth}}, {{cog|fa|زغال|tr=zoġāl||live coal}}), from {{m|ine-pro|*ǵwelH-||to glow, burn}} (compare {{cog|lt|žvìlti||to twinkle, glow}}, {{cog|sa|ज्वलति||to burn, glow}}).

